<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull], [asker_faction_leaderTitle] of [asker_faction_name], has sent us a message. Apparently, [siteFaction_pawnsPlural] based in a nearby camp have been raiding their caravans. The camp is controlled by [siteFaction_name].\n\n[asker_nameDef] is asking us to destroy the camp, which means eliminating all enemies and turrets. [asker_label] says that [sitePart0_description].\n\nIf we succeed, [allRewardsDescriptions]</li>
  -->
  <OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
    <li>questDescription->[asker_nameFull], [asker_faction_leaderTitle] der Fraktion '[asker_faction_name]', hat uns eine Nachricht geschickt.\n\nSo wie es aussieht, überfallen [siteFaction_pawnsPlural] von einem nahegelegenen Lager aus ihre Karawanen. Das Lager gehört zu der Fraktion '[siteFaction_name]'.\n\n[asker_nameDef] hat uns gebeten, das Lager zu zerstören. Genauer: Es sollen alle Gegner und Geschütztürme ausgeschaltet werden. [asker_label] meint, dass [sitePart0_description].\n\nWenn wir Erfolg haben, wird [allRewardsDescriptions]</li>
    <li>singleThingDescriptionOptional(priority=1)->\n\n[singleThingDescription]</li>
    <li>singleThingDescriptionOptional-></li>
  </OpportunitySite_BanditCamp.questDescriptionRules.rulesStrings>
  <!-- EN:
    <li>questName->[asker_nameDef]'s Camp Bounty</li>
    <li>questName->Camp of [enemyFaction_pawnsPlural]</li>
